        <item>
            <title>【评测】Mac mini M4 2024：进阶用家最应该买的 Apple 电脑，效能、日常应用详细评测分析</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/07/mac-mini-2024-review/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mac-mini-2024-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/07/mac-mini-2024-review/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:03:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mac]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini M4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273818</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 一口气推出全新 M4 系列的 MacBook Pro、Mac mini 和 iMac，当中 Mac mini 以全新轻巧外型吸引全球 Apple 用家注意。实际上它内置的 M4 / M4 Pro 处理器，将这个只有手掌大小的盒子，成为可替代以往坐枱式电脑，就同有了 Mini PC 大家不去黄金砌机一样，成为电脑上的一个革命（起码在 Apple 电脑来说）。这款小型电脑在硬件上有显著提升，运行日常设计、影片剪辑软件都非常够做，更支援 Apple Intelligence 提升工作效率，是追求效能，但不是追求终极效能的用家之中，性价比超强的选择。以下将详细评测 Mac mini，为你说明为何「进阶用家」应用要买的是 Mac mini 而不是其他 Apple 电脑。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-scaled.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273834" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03649-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>相关影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_85048"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G9wF-ei92Ao?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>进一步精简的外型设计</h2><p>Mac mini 已成为了一部「高性价比版本的 Mac Studio」。</p><p>早前外国已有跑分，证明 M4 Pro 版 Mac mini 的 CPU 跑分能够胜过 M2 Ultra 的 Mac Studio 达到 25%。这就反映了如果你对电脑效能的需要，只是图像处理、影片／声音剪辑、创作等用途，而非大型电影制作，考虑到价钱，Mac mini 是一个性价比极高的选择。当然 Mac Studio 有它的好处，这些我们都知道，但考虑到当时 M2 Ultra 版的 Mac Studio 售价是 HK$32,999，而今次新机就算是 M4 Pro 版售价都只是 HK$10,599，很粗暴的比较之下，大家发现如果可以牺性某些 Mac Studio 的特点，Mac mini 变成了很多进阶用家直接的选择。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03664-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273885 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110792516-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>特别是对于小编来说，平时需要剪片、上网看网页、处理图片，以往 M2 年代也是觉得很够用。像我这类接受不到平价电脑，但又不至于要求一部怪兽级电脑的人来说，Mac mini 就非常吸引。像小编这类用家，好多以前都用 iMac 27 吋。不过自从 Apple 不再出 iMac 27 吋之后，大家就将目光转移到 Mac mini。今时今日 Mac mini 在 Apple 电脑中的角色，已经同以前大大不同。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110720h21-3.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲重量只有约 650g 的 Mac mini，可以带去旅行驳酒店电视，当电脑用或睇片</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03663-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲实际长阔度只有一只精妙滑鼠多一点</p><p>新一代的 Mac mini 体积缩小了超过一半，由上代的 7.75&#215;7.75 吋压缩至仅 5&#215;5 吋，从以往的扁平造型转变成更立体的方砖设计，类似于缩小版的 Mac Studio，重量只有约 650 克。这种轻巧设计无疑更适合需要节省空间的用家，你甚至可以 mount 在电脑荧幕之后。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010-694x509.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010-694x509.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire0010.jpg 1227w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire001211536x864.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这是上次我们借用的 Mac mini 2023 版本，可见要放下它还是不易。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03644-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 Mac mini 2024 版本，一体感更好，你会发现桌面多了好多空间。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03650-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
